result.name: organogram-hm-treasury
result.notes:
Organogram (organisation chart) showing all staff roles. Names and salaries are also listed for the Senior Civil Servants.

Organogram data is released by all central government departments and their agencies since 2010. Snapshots for 31st March, 30th June, 30th September and 31st December are published each quarter. The published data is validated and released in CSV format and OGL-licensed for reuse. For more information about this series, see: http://guidance.data.gov.uk/organogram-data.html

organization.name: hm-treasury
organization.title: HM Treasury
organization.description:
HM Treasury is the government’s economic and finance ministry, maintaining control over public spending, setting the direction of the UK’s economic policy and working to achieve strong and sustainable economic growth.

HMT is a ministerial department, supported by 8 agencies and public bodies.

https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-treasury
